==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Leafless
<hw>Leaf"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no leaves or foliage;
bearing no foliage.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Leafless</xex> groves.⟦rdquo⟧
<au>Cowper.</au> -- <wordforms><wf>Leaf"less*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Leafless plants</b></col>, <cd>plants having no foliage,
though leaves may be present in the form of scales and bracts. See
<er>Leaf</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 1 and 2.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leaflet</ent>⟦br⟧
